### Basic usage

```jsx
<ExpandCollapse
  className="ExpandCollapse-stories-module_storybookExpandCollapse"
  title="Expand collapse"
>
  <Text
    maxLines={2}
    type="text2"
  >
    Insert here any component that you want, here is a robot for you
  </Text>
  <Icon
    icon={function noRefCheck(){}}
    iconSize={40}
    iconType="svg"
  />
</ExpandCollapse>
```

### Without borders

```jsx
<ExpandCollapse
  hideBorder
  title="Without borders"
  className={styles.storybookExpandCollapse}
>
  <Text type="text2" maxLines={2}>
    Insert here any component that you want
  </Text>
</ExpandCollapse>
```